  "description": "Improves item stack sizes (With Configurability)",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>SimpleStack</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Improves the stack sizes of a few items I thought were a hassle to only have a single amount of (minecarts and [all colour] beds).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SBt81nPT/images/5f9606d0581a94c966e98d96ccf343d9785de6d1.png\" width=\"162\" height=\"152\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> Also allows for you to add your own items with specified stack sizes in the config (simplestack-common.toml).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SBt81nPT/images/e5b45db16727a512239662960675ea8c7b1aaa22.png\" /></span></p>",
